<hw>Lake</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G. <ets>laken</ets>.]</ety>
<def>A kind of fine white linen, formerly in use.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

