==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Lake
<hw>Lake</hw> <pr>(l⟦amac⟧k)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>l⟦amac⟧can</ets>, <ets>l⟦ae⟧can</ets>, to spring, jump,
<ets>l⟦amac⟧c</ets> play, sport, or fr. Icel. <ets>leika</ets> to play,
